<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>{{ title }}</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #f5f7fb;
      color: #1f2937;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 1080px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 32px 20px 64px;
    }
    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1f2937, #374151);
      color: white;
      padding: 32px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.18);
    }
    .hero h1 { margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 32px; }
    .hero p { margin: 0; opacity: 0.85; }
    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .card {
      background: white;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .metric {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }
    h2 { margin-top: 0; }
    li { margin-bottom: 8px; }
    img {
      max-width: 100%;
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin: 10px 0 22px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    table {
      border-collapse: collapse;
      width: 100%;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }
    th, td {
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      padding: 8px 10px;
      text-align: left;
    }
    th { background: #f3f4f6; }
    .footer { color: #6b7280; margin-top: 24px; font-size: 14px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="container">
    <section class="hero">
      <h1>{{ title }}</h1>
      <p>生成时间：{{ generated_at }}</p>
    </section>

    <section class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <div>数据行数</div>
        <div class="metric">{{ profile.row_count }}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div>数据列数</div>
        <div class="metric">{{ profile.column_count }}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div>核心指标总量</div>
        <div class="metric">{{ "%.2f"|format(profile.target_summary.sum if profile.target_summary else 0) }}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div>核心指标均值</div>
        <div class="metric">{{ "%.2f"|format(profile.target_summary.mean if profile.target_summary else 0) }}</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h2>一、分析任务计划</h2>
      <ul>
        {% for item in plan %}<li>{{ item }}</li>{% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h2>二、核心洞察</h2>
      <ol>
        {% for item in insights %}<li>{{ item }}</li>{% endfor %}
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h2>三、关键图表</h2>
      {% for path in chart_paths %}
        <img src="{{ path }}" alt="chart" />
      {% endfor %}
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h2>四、明细表</h2>
      {% for name, rows in tables.items() %}
        <h3>{{ name }}</h3>
        {% if rows and rows[0] is mapping %}
          <table>
            <thead>
              <tr>{% for key in rows[0].keys() %}<th>{{ key }}</th>{% endfor %}</tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              {% for row in rows[:10] %}
                <tr>{% for value in row.values() %}<td>{{ value }}</td>{% endfor %}</tr>
              {% endfor %}
            </tbody>
          </table>
        {% else %}
          <p>无数据。</p>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </section>

    <section class="card">
      <h2>五、结论与建议</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>建议重点关注贡献度最高的分组维度，结合业务目标进行资源倾斜。</li>
        <li>对异常日期或异常指标进行复盘，判断是业务机会、数据质量问题还是突发风险。</li>
        <li>可将本系统接入数据库、邮件或企业微信，实现自动化日报推送。</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <div class="footer">Generated by Multi-Agent Data Insight Daily Report System</div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
